summary: The moon is changed to the likeness of Dolan.
descriptionHtml:
The moon is changed to the likeness of Dolan. It\'s a quick job, so i don\'t know how good it works, any bugs and such.

Instalation: just throw the files in your Data folder as usual.

Compatibility: incompatible with any mod that changes moon textures.

Side note: i\'m known as atikabubu elsewhere, i just don\'t have the guts to bug the admin to change my nickname :S
